Alex Skuby https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alex_Skuby 0 Alex Skuby (born December 27, 1972) is an American actor who has appeared in film and television. He is most known for playing Doug Pruzan, Carrie's boss and a lawyer at her Manhattan law firm on The King of Queens.
